1. No harassment, sexism, racism, or bigotry of any kind.
   This is a zero-tolerance policy. Violators will be purged.

2. Player killing is allowed for characters over level 10, and only
   between characters within +/- 3 levels of each other.
   Werewolves and Vampires are not considered "mortal" and may be
   staked without OUTLAW flagging. Killing an OUTLAW carries no
   additional penalty.

3. Do not exploit bugs. Report them to an immortal immediately.
   Exploiting bugs for personal gain is grounds for deletion.

4. Stealing from other players requires OUTLAW status. You may NEVER
   junk stolen equipment -- this represents an irreplacable loss and
   will result in removal from the game.

5. Stealing items from other players' corpses is prohibited, except
   when recovering an item that was stolen from you.

6. Do not attempt to flee combat by purposefully cutting your link.
   You will not be reimbursed for experience or equipment lost this way.

7. Do not abuse multi-playing. Moving stolen items between your
   OUTLAW character and non-outlaw multis will result in flagging.
   Repeated abuse will result in deletion.

8. Immortals reserve the right to handle disputes, reimbursements,
   and discipline at their discretion. Their word is final.

9. Have fun. Explore. Make friends. Die horribly. Try again.
